N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 4 ยง 90.6 - Employment extension

State Regulations

This Part shall not be construed to authorize or require
extension of any employment beyond the time at which it would otherwise
terminate by operation of law, rule or regulation. Notes
